{"tid":1686798,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚8點 民記要人！","createTime":"2019-11-01T11:20:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T19:03:54.000Z","uid":325953,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"ed013173d62c59574152f84e79220127096a7ce1","tid":1686798,"uid":325953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T11:20:43.000Z","msg":"緊急<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />民間記者會今晚（1/11）八點需要大家準時收睇直播<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二十二次民間記者會（1/11 晚上八點）嘅主題係「看不見的人道危機」，將首度披露其中一名因警濫暴濫權、醫護白色恐怖而精神受創嘅抗爭者喺呢場運動期間嘅精神健康，令大家從另外一個角度深入了解抗爭者背後所承受無人知曉無法體會嘅巨大壓力同情緒困擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位香港人，知唔知道點解呢位抗爭者願意忍痛揭露自己血淋淋嘅心靈傷口畀所有人知道？目的只有一個&mdash;&mdash;就係希望多D香港人了解佢哋嘅精神健康實況，俾多D鼓勵同正能量佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔係唔撐呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今晚（1/11）晚上八點，約定大家直播見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望各位香港人將呢段Message廣發至各大社交平台（例如Telegram，Facebook，WhatsApp，Instagram等等）並通知俾身邊所有朋友今日（1/11）八點準時收看直播<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可於以下或其他頻道收看直播：<br />\n基進報導：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/radicalhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fradicalhk%2F&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvMQ0GhOv7yEvjYTsEPvBCF8%3D&h=14ae4c38\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/radicalhk/</a> <br />\n反送中直播：<a href=\"http://www.hklivegroup.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hklivegroup.com%2F&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvMQ0GhOv7yEvjYTsEPvBCF8%3D&h=cffacdd7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hklivegroup.com/</a> （首次觀睇需要下載加密插件）<br />\n立場新聞：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww